    <item>
      <title>Never Type Your Password Again: Automatic SSH Logins in Windows Terminal</title>
      <link>https://dennys.github.io/en/doc/network/ssh-login-automatically-windows-terminal/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://dennys.github.io/en/doc/network/ssh-login-automatically-windows-terminal/</guid>
      <description>
        
          
            &lt;h2 id=&#34;requirement&#34;&gt;Requirement&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;procedures&#34;&gt;Procedures&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Generate key&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Execute &lt;code&gt;ssh-keygen&lt;/code&gt; and generate the file &lt;code&gt;id_rsa&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-cmd&#34; data-lang=&#34;cmd&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;C&lt;span class=&#34;p&#34;&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;nl&#34;&gt;\Users\dennys&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;c1&#34;&gt;&amp;gt;ssh-keygen&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Generating public/private rsa key pair.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Enter file in which to save the key (C:\Users\dennys/.ssh/id_rsa):
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The content of id_rsa is like the following.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;ln&#34;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;ssh-rsa AAAAB******************&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;==&lt;/span&gt; dennys@mypc123
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Put the key on Linux&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Open the file &lt;code&gt;~/.ssh/authorized_keys&lt;/code&gt; and paste the content of id_rsa into it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Test automatically login&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute &lt;code&gt;ssh name@host&lt;/code&gt;, you don&#39;t need to input password any more.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Configuratino Windows Terminal&lt;/p&gt;
          
          
        
